  "remarks": "\n The Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that Yadollah BOUALI is an involved person under The Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 on the basis of the following ground: BOUALI is or has been involved in the commission of serious human rights violations or abuses in Iran, specifically violating the right to freedom of expression and peaceful assembly, and the right to life.\n",
